#: 00604:7
msgid "It happened one night."
msgstr "Eso ocurrió una noche."

#: 00604:10
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Hey, Kazushi.\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"Oye, Kazushi.\""

#: 00604:11
msgid "After dinner one night, Appo spoke to me like he was in some kind of trouble."
msgstr "Parece como si tuviese algún problema."

#: 00604:12
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What's up?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Qué pasa?\""

#: 00604:15
# 'mamar alguna teta', 'chupar alguna teta', 'morder algunos pezones'
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Do you want to go suck on some tits?\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"¿No te gustaría mamar alguna teta?\""

#: 00604:16
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"......What!?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿¡Qué...!?\""

#: 00604:17
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Aren't you dying to suck a pair of tits?\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"Yo me muero por hacerlo.\""

#: 00604:18
msgid "What the hell is he talking about? I've been friends with Appo ages, but he still manages to say the weirdest things every now and then."
msgstr "¿De qué está hablando?"

#: 00604:21
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Tits, man, tits! Ever since we got here, we've been surrounded by tits every single day, but all we can do is look?!\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"Estoy harto de limitarme a mirarlas desde que llegamos.\""

#: 00604:22
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Well, of course. Hold on...I don't like that look in your eyes?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Has perdido la cabeza...?\""

#: 00604:25
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"I can't take it anymore! I want to suck some tits! Tits! Tits!\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"¡Ya no puedo aguantarlo más!\n"
"¡Quiero tetas!\""

#: 00604:26
msgid "He was lying on the floor kicking his arms and legs like a spoiled child. Is he going to be okay?"
msgstr "Es como un niño mimado en una juguetería."

#: 00604:27
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Calm down! Don't lose control of yourself!\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¡Tranquilízate!\""

#: 00604:30
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"We're roomies, right?\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"Somos compañeros de habitación, ¿no?\""

#: 00604:31
msgid "He leaned his head up towards me from where he was curled up on the floor."
msgstr ""

#: 00604:32
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"And your point is?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Y qué?\""

#: 00604:35
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Let me suck your tits.\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"Enséñame tus tetas.\""

#: 00604:36
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"...the fuck?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Qué...?\""

#: 00604:37
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"...\""

#: 00604:38
msgid "He was dead serious, and I was frightened."
msgstr "Está empezando a asustarme."

#: 00604:39
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Hey, calm down man? Appo, I don't have the kind of tits you're looking for.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Yo no tengo tetas. Soy un tío.\""

#: 00604:42
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"........................Yeah, you're right.\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"Ya veo...\n"
"Tienes razón.\""

#: 00604:43
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Phew...are you back to normal now?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Ya has vuelto...?\""

#: 00604:44
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"I'm gonna go suck Daigo's.\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"Voy a pedírselo a Daigo.\""

#: 00604:45
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Qué?\""

#: 00604:48
msgid "He dragged himself up off the floor and hobbled over to the other room."
msgstr "Se levantó y se dirigió a la habitación de al lado."

#: 00604:50
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Is he serious?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Lo dice en serio?\""

#: 00604:51
msgid ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"Hey, what's up, Appo?\n"
"......AAAAHHHHH!!! WHAT ARE YOU DOING!?\""
msgstr ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"¿¡Qué pasa Appo-!?\n"
"¿¡Qué estás haciendo!?\""

#: 00604:52
msgid "I heard Daigo screaming."
msgstr "Oí a Daigo gritar."

#: 00604:53
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"This is hell.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Estoy en el infierno.\""

#: 00604:54
msgid "I put my hands over my ears and hid under my bed covers. It's almost nine o'clock; still too early to sleep."
msgstr "Me tapé los oídos y me metí en la cama."

#: 00604:55
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
" *yawn*"
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"*Bostezando*"

#: 00604:56
msgid "I stretched myself out. Every since I got here, I feel like I've been sleepy every day."
msgstr ""

#: 00604:57
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Maybe I'm just tired.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Quizá esté cansado.\""

#: 00604:58
msgid "Mentally. Maybe spending every day surrounded by women like this is forcing me to be more nervous than ever."
msgstr "Creo que estoy agotado por el esfuerzo de acostumbrarme al nuevo entorno."

#: 00604:59
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I should go to bed early tonight.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Hoy debería acostarme temprano.\""

#: 00604:62
msgid "I closed my eyes."
msgstr "Cerré los ojos."

#: 00604:66
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Huh?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿¡!?\""

#: 00604:67
msgid "I think I hear footsteps outside the dorm."
msgstr "Me ha parecido oír pasos afuera."

#: 00604:68
msgid "Somebody's outside."
msgstr "Hay alguien fiera."

#: 00604:69
msgid "It wasn't that late, so it wouldn't be odd, but for some reason those footsteps made me curious."
msgstr "Todavía no es muy tarde, pero el sonido hace que me pregunte quién es."

#: 00604:70
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Who could that be?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Quién podría ser?\""

#: 00604:71
msgid "I looked outside through the window and saw a tiny, familiar silhouette."
msgstr "Miré al exterior por la ventana."

#: 00604:72
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"That's......\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Es...\""

#: 00604:73
msgid "What is she doing out there at this time again? My drowsiness quickly went away."
msgstr "¿Qué está haciendo por aquí otra vez?"

#: 00604:77
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Natsume-chan?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Natsume?\""

#: 00604:80
msgid "When I called out to her, she turned around with her usual expressionless face."
msgstr "Fui fuera a ver qué estaba haciendo."

#: 00604:83
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Oh, it's you, Haruma.\n"
"I'm tired of seeing your face.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Eres tú otra vez.\n"
"Estoy cansada de verte la cara.\""

#: 00604:84
msgid "She was already fed up with me."
msgstr "Eso fue lo primero que dijo."

#: 00604:85
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Already? We've only seen each other a few times.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Ya? Si solo nos hemos visto en contadas ocasiones.\""

#: 00604:86
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"And I'm already sick of you.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Las suficientes para cansarme de ti.\""

#: 00604:87
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Already? That's too fast.\""
msgstr ""

#: 00604:88
msgid "That was all she had to say, and then she seemed to lose interest in me. She kept her eyes on her feet as she started walking away."
msgstr "Eso es todo lo que me dijo antes de continuar su andadura nocturna."

#: 00604:89
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Why are you taking a walk at this time of night, anyways?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"De todas formas, ¿qué haces paseando a esta hora del día?\""

#: 00604:90
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"No reason.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"No hay motivo.\""

#: 00604:91
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"There's got to be a reason.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Tiene que haber algún motivo.\""

#: 00604:94
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"...\""

#: 00604:95
msgid "She ignored me. She must think I'm nagging her. Oh well, I'm used to the cold shoulder."
msgstr "Continúa ignorándome."

#: 00604:96
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"You're sure a night-owl, Natsume-chan. Didn't I meet you for the first time around this time of night? Are you able to get up OK in the morning?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Era sobre esta hora cuando te conocí. ¿No te cuesta levantarte por las mañanas?\""

#: 00604:97
msgid "She turned around."
msgstr "Se giró."

#: 00604:100
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Shut up, Haruma.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Cállate, Kazushi.\""

#: 00604:101
msgid "She scolded me. I guess she didn't want to be lectured."
msgstr "Supongo que no quieren que le den ningún sermón."

#: 00604:102
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Could it be that you're looking for something?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Quizá es que estás buscando algo?\""

#: 00604:103
msgid "That's the only thing I could think she was doing."
msgstr "Es lo único que se me ocurre que pueda estar haciendo."

#: 00604:104
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"If you're looking for something, I'll help. Is it something important?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Quieres que te ayude?\""

#: 00604:107
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"...\""

#: 00604:108
msgid "She stopped and looked at me."
msgstr "Se paró y me miró."

#: 00604:111
msgid "...and took a big sigh."
msgstr "Y exhaló un largo suspiro..."

#: 00604:112
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I don't remember doing anything to make you sigh.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No creo haber hecho nada para que suspires.\""

#: 00604:113
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"And that's one reason why you're stupid, Haruma.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Es por eso por lo que eres tan estúpido.\""

#: 00604:114
msgid "She nodded her head."
msgstr "Está asintiendo con la cabeza."

#: 00604:115
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Stop talking to me like that!\n"
"I'm your sempai, so show me some respect!\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¡Deja de hablarme así!\n"
"Soy más mayor que tú, ¡muestra algo de respeto!\""

#: 00604:118
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"...\""

#: 00604:119
msgid "Oops, I think I said that too loud."
msgstr "No pretendía alzar la voz."

#: 00604:122
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\".........sniff.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"¿¡...!?\""

#: 00604:123
msgid "She started shaking."
msgstr "Ha empezado a temblar."

#: 00604:124
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Hh......sniff.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"*A punto de llorar*"

#: 00604:125
msgid "Then her eyes started to get watery. This makes it look I'm bullying her."
msgstr "Oh, no... Está a punto de llorar."

#: 00604:126
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Don't cry, okay?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No vas a llorar, ¿no?\""

#: 00604:127
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"I'm not......crying......\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"No estoy... llorando...\""

#: 00604:128
msgid "She's already half crying."
msgstr "Ya está medio llorando."

#: 00604:129
msgid "I hope no one's watching this."
msgstr "Espero que nadie esté presenciando esto."

#: 00604:130
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Please don't cry.\n"
"I promise I won't raise my voice again.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Por favor, no llores.\n"
"Te prometo que no volveré a levantarte la voz.\""

#: 00604:131
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"I'm not crying......don't treat me like a kid......stupid......\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"No estoy llorando... No me trates como a un niño... estúpido...\""

#: 00604:132
msgid "She rubbed her eyes as she insulted me. The tip of her nose was getting red. She was clearly crying."
msgstr "Está llorando un montón, tiene los ojos rojos."

#: 00604:133
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I'm sorry.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Lo siento.\""

#: 00604:134
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Don't apologize! I didn't cry so, why are you apologizing?\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"No te disculpes, porque no he llorado.\""

#: 00604:135
msgid "She refused to admit she was crying. What a stubborn girl. I'm glad she has yet to realize that tears are a woman's weapon."
msgstr "Menuda niña más cabezota."

#: 00604:136
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Here, let me help you look for it as penance.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Venga, deja que te ayude a encontrar lo que estás buscando.\""

#: 00604:137
msgid "I didn't know what she was looking for but I started looking around. I should be able to find it if she dropped something."
msgstr "No sé lo que está buscando, pero empiezo a buscar por los alrededores."

#: 00604:138
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Hey, could you tell me what you dropped? It's hard to look if I don't know.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Oye. Me tendrías que decir al menos lo que se te ha caído.\""

#: 00604:141
msgid "She gave me another big sigh at my persistence."
msgstr "Vuelve a exhalar un largo suspiro."

#: 00604:142
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"If you really want to help me......\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Si de verdad quieres ayudarme...\""

#: 00604:145
msgid "Her pure eyes caught my eyes."
msgstr "Sus ojos puros cautivan los míos."

#: 00604:146
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Find me.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Encuéntrame.\""

#: 00604:147
msgid "I didn't understand what she meant, but her eyes were telling me she was serious."
msgstr "No entendí lo que quería decir, pero sus ojos me decían que lo decía en serio."

#: 00604:148
msgid "What did she mean by \"find me\"?"
msgstr "¿Qué quieres decir con \"encuéntrame\"?"

#: 00604:149
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Find you what?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Encontrarte el qué?\""

#: 00604:152
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Find. Me. What else?\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"A mí. Qué si no.\""

#: 00604:153
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"But Natsume-chan, you're...\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Bueno. Ahí estás...\""

#: 00604:154
msgid "She was right in front of me."
msgstr "Está justo delante de mí."

#: 00604:155
msgid "I didn't say it, because I realized she'd tell me that thought was stupid. Maybe it's some kind of metaphor?"
msgstr "No lo dije, porque pensé que se refería a algún tipo de metáfora."

#: 00604:158
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"If you can't understand what I mean then don't bother. It's impossible for you, Haruma.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Si no puedes comprender a lo que me refiero, no te molestes.\""

#: 00604:159
msgid "Natsume-chan looked dejected. Her voice was quiet too."
msgstr "Parece decepcionada."

#: 00604:160
msgid "But I didn't understand what Natsume-chan meant. What part of Natsume-chan am I supposed to find?"
msgstr "Pero no entendí a lo que se refería."

#: 00604:161
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"All right.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Está bien.\""

#: 00604:162
msgid "I don't know what she means, but I'll remember this."
msgstr "Ya lo averiguaré más adelante."

#: 00604:165
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"You can forget about it.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Puedes olvidarlo.\""

#: 00604:166
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No, I'll be sure to remember it.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No. Averiguaré lo que querías decir.\""

#: 00604:167
msgid "I may not understand now, but there will come a day when I do. I'll remember what she said tonight so I can be ready when it comes."
msgstr "Algún día entender'a lo que se refería."
